      "description": "Predicted MIH using power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger damage accumulation compared against the Herbertson et al. 2015 inter-laboratory dataset. CFD predicted MIH = 4.8 vs measured MIH = 5.1 (relative deviation 5.9%). Comparator is widely cited, geometry-matched, and was used in the FDA benchmark round-robin; we therefore consider it the authoritative reference. Acceptance band +/-25% satisfied with margin.",
